# Miscellaneous

* du -hs <folder>                               - size of a folder
* pwgen <number>                                - password generation
* tree -d -L 2                                  - tree show only directories and only 2 deep
* crunch 5 5 xyz                                - generate wordlist with min length 5, max length 5 and containing only xyz
* fix_caddy                                     - fixes permissions for caddy
* rename '<substring>' '<substition>' *         - rename all filenames; replace <substring> with <subsitution>
* check <file> <md5|sha256|sha1 checksum>       - checks a file against a checksum

# SSH
* see logged in users:
    * who
    * who -a
    * netstat -tnpa | grep 'ESTABLISHED.*sshd'
    * ps ax | grep sshd
